songs.title: Anything Could Happen (Finals)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Have you ever had a dream become a reality?
Have you ever seen the impossible become possible?
And now you know the truth
Anything could happen
Anything could happen
Anything could happen
Anything could happen
Anything could

[Verse: Lauren & Camila]
After the war we said we'd fight together
I guess we thought that's just what humans do
But now I've seen it through
And now I know the truth

[Hook: All]
Anything could happen
Anything could happen
Anything could happen
Anything could happen
Anything could

[Bridge: Dinah & Camila]
Baby, I'll give you anything you need
I'll give you anything you need, yeah
I'll give you anything you need
I know it's going to be
I know it's going to be
I know it's going to be
I know it's going to be
I know it's going to be
I know it's going to be alright

[Chorus: All]
Since we found out
Since we found out
Anything could happen
Anything could happen
Anything could happen
Anything could happen
Anything could
